        <span style="font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:rgba(248,244,238,0.6);">Shop Pay · Klarna · PayPal · Visa</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  {%- comment -%} ═════════ 16. FOOTER ═════════ {%- endcomment -%}
  <footer class="lp4-footer">
    <div class="lp4__shell">
      <div class="lp4-footer__logo">UBurn</div>
      <p class="lp4-footer__disclaimer">Dietary supplement containing konjac glucomannan. Glucomannan supports satiety as part of a balanced lifestyle.* Recommended use: 3g/day in 3 doses of 1g with 1-2 large glasses of water before meals. Not a substitute for a balanced diet. Not recommended during pregnancy or breastfeeding.</p>
